lass="module-header"><h3>主办方</h3></div><div class="module-body"><ul class="items"><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/topic/20082571" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='t$t$20082571'><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-0781b2214bf66133379ced59708811c0_l.jpg" alt="户外探险杂志" class="avatar d50"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/topic/20082571" class="name" data-hovercard='t$t$20082571'>户外探险杂志</a><div class="bio">举办过 1 场圆桌</div></div></div><div class="item-body"><p class="description">《户外探险》 于2001年创刊，是一本关注本质生活的杂志，倡导以成熟的方式亲近自然。通过专业品质向大众呈现户外运动各个方面，如深度自助旅行、登山、驾车、摄影、探险等。<br>目前已发展为集微信、微博、线上FM、活动定制、视频制作、培训、期刊与图书出版等为一体的全媒体立体传播平台。<br>于2006年首创的户外运动界最具影响力最权威的“中国户外金犀牛奖”评选活动 ，已经成为业界精英的年度盛会。<br>团队正在以更高的标准、更新的形式，向更多人传达着我们的声音：户外是一种生活方式，探险是一种生活态度，让阳光和风进入本质生活。</p></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/topic/19793502" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='t$t$19793502'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-1003bb2fb402f1b21f60b7d5ca555b71_l.jpg" alt="知乎圆桌" class="avatar d50"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/topic/19793502" class="name" data-hovercard='t$t$19793502'>知乎圆桌</a><div class="bio">举办过 255 场圆桌</div></div></div><div class="item-body"><p class="description">知乎发起的在线嘉宾讨论，详情请点击：<a href="http://www.zhihu.com/question/20886632" data-editable="true" data-title="什么是「知乎圆桌」？如何参与" class="">什么是「知乎圆桌」？如何参与</a>？<br>圆桌页面：<a href="http://www.zhihu.com/roundtable" data-editable="true" data-title="活动">活动列表</a></p></div></li></ul></div></div><div class="module guests"><div class="module-header"><h3>嘉宾</h3></div><div class="module-body"><ul class="items"><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/xing-she-cong-cong" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$xing-she-cong-cong'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e371c34cce9880e5745a528fc5ed8616_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="行摄匆匆"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/dengshantubu/xing-she-cong-cong/answers" class="answers text-muted">3 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/xing-she-cong-cong" data-hovercard='p$t$xing-she-cong-cong'>行摄匆匆</a><div class="bio">徒步中国 <span class="bull">&bull;</span> 创始人</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/zi-jun-vivian" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$zi-jun-vivian'><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-8d7795dfc48dfb62962df29ca6e34e8e_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="子君Vivian"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/dengshantubu/zi-jun-vivian/answers" class="answers text-muted">7 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/zi-jun-vivian" data-hovercard='p$t$zi-jun-vivian'>子君Vivian</a><div class="bio">中国首位登顶珠峰南坡&amp;amp;北坡女性</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/seven721" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$seven721'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a611fe85e2d4b32f922b619302aa96ec_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="江文韬"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/dengshantubu/seven721/answers" class="answers text-muted">2 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/seven721" data-hovercard='p$t$seven721'>江文韬</a><span class="icon icon-badge-best_answerer icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$优秀回答者"></span><div class="bio">星野摄影脑残粉/微博&amp;amp;微信@imX的星空笔记</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/gu-niao-niao-57" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$gu-niao-niao-57'><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ad8df45df8e54a2129b96079b382718e_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="古袅袅"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/dengshantubu/gu-niao-niao-57/answers" class="answers text-muted">3 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/gu-niao-niao-57" data-hovercard='p$t$gu-niao-niao-57'>古袅袅</a><div class="bio">政府 <span class="bull">&bull;</span> 公务员</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/xiao-yu-90-47-7" class="item-link" tabindex